text: Josef Švec (born 20 November 1935) is a Czechoslovak rower. He competed at the 1956 Summer Olympics in Melbourne with the men's eight where they were eliminated in the semi-final. ==References== Category:1935 births Category:Living people Category:Czechoslovak male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Czechoslovakia Category:Rowers at the 1956 Summer Olympics Category:European Rowing Championships medalists
